title: Aliabad-e Yek, Rafsanjan
text: Aliabad-e Yek (, also <a href="Romanize">Romanize</a>d as ‘Alīābād-e Yek; also known as ‘Alīābād) is a village in <a href="Sarcheshmeh%20Rural%20District">Sarcheshmeh Rural District</a>, in the <a href="Central%20District%20%28Rafsanjan%20County%29">Central District</a> of <a href="Rafsanjan%20County">Rafsanjan County</a>, <a href="Kerman%20Province">Kerman Province</a>, <a href="Iran">Iran</a>. At the 2006 census, its population was 12, in 6 families.
